    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a0027143-d45b-58be-8f69-f2d6dba5bbf6","excerpt":"Airport Observations ✈️ I was at the Delhi Airport a couple of months ago, early morning flight, sleep deprived, bored, so I decided to do some people-watching…","html":"<p><a href=\"\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 820px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.82926829268293%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"airport chaos\"\n        title=\"airport chaos\"\n        src=\"/static/71f976a11af8f14910ef9ffa6c20d1a4/9f82e/airport-chaos.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/71f976a11af8f14910ef9ffa6c20d1a4/85860/airport-chaos.png 205w,\n/static/71f976a11af8f14910ef9ffa6c20d1a4/d68e4/airport-chaos.png 410w,\n/static/71f976a11af8f14910ef9ffa6c20d1a4/9f82e/airport-chaos.png 820w,\n/static/71f976a11af8f14910ef9ffa6c20d1a4/0d0e4/airport-chaos.png 1230w,\n/static/71f976a11af8f14910ef9ffa6c20d1a4/71c1d/airport-chaos.png 1536w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></a></p>\n<h2>Airport Observations ✈️</h2>\n<p>I was at the Delhi Airport a couple of months ago, early morning flight, sleep deprived, bored, so I decided to do some people-watching. Airports are a mix of chaos and order, full of stories colliding in real time hellos, goodbyes, nerves, excitement. While waiting for my flight, I found myself observing the little dramas, habits, and quirks unfolding around me.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Airports probably have the highest density of cute and fashionable people, like everyone got a memo that this was a runway show.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 735px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2fa19533589460ea81ae14e8fbac0dfc/7608e/cuties.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.8048780487805%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"cuties at the airport\"\n        title=\"cuties at the airport\"\n        src=\"/static/2fa19533589460ea81ae14e8fbac0dfc/7608e/cuties.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2fa19533589460ea81ae14e8fbac0dfc/85860/cuties.png 205w,\n/static/2fa19533589460ea81ae14e8fbac0dfc/d68e4/cuties.png 410w,\n/static/2fa19533589460ea81ae14e8fbac0dfc/7608e/cuties.png 735w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">cuties at the airport</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Class divide:</strong> economy vs business, priority vs normal boarding, basically rich people vs the rest of us pretending to be patient.</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Emotions flying everywhere:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Families reuniting after long.</li>\n<li>Folks going away from families for long.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>People <em>pretending</em> to work on laptops aka staring at Excel sheets while scrolling Instagram.</li>\n<li>People actually working on laptops, RIP to their work-life balance.</li>\n<li>\n<p>The WFH warriors secretly traveling without telling their team “Sorry guys, I’m facing network issues” while sipping mojito at the airport lounge.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/39c9e322d77f3fb2a29df93eb3d2c37c/0b533/wfh.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"people working from home\"\n        title=\"people working from home\"\n        src=\"/static/39c9e322d77f3fb2a29df93eb3d2c37c/0b533/wfh.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/39c9e322d77f3fb2a29df93eb3d2c37c/85860/wfh.png 205w,\n/static/39c9e322d77f3fb2a29df93eb3d2c37c/d68e4/wfh.png 410w,\n/static/39c9e322d77f3fb2a29df93eb3d2c37c/0b533/wfh.png 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">people working from home</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n</li>\n<li>First-time fliers: some look terrified, some are excited.</li>\n<li>Proud middle-class kids taking their parents on a flight for the first time!</li>\n<li>People walking around acting 20% cooler than they actually are, sunglasses inside, of course.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Uncles watching WhatsApp videos on full volume without earphones, national nuisance since 2010.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 503px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cb34ed740df2983a3d9520b26bf4708b/a4078/uncles.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 98.53658536585365%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"loud videos\"\n        title=\"loud videos\"\n        src=\"/static/cb34ed740df2983a3d9520b26bf4708b/a4078/uncles.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cb34ed740df2983a3d9520b26bf4708b/85860/uncles.png 205w,\n/static/cb34ed740df2983a3d9520b26bf4708b/d68e4/uncles.png 410w,\n/static/cb34ed740df2983a3d9520b26bf4708b/a4078/uncles.png 503w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 503px) 100vw, 503px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">loud videos</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n</li>\n<li>Half the crowd debating whether that ₹400 coffee is worth it or not and I’m simply eating the Aloo Prathas my mom made ❤️.</li>\n<li>Luggage check: trying to guess people’s net worth by their bags and wondering what <em>you</em> are doing wrong with your life.</li>\n<li>Kids screaming like they’re auditioning for a horror movie, both at the airport and mid-air.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Sleep-deprived zombies everywhere. Basically, the terminal is one giant group yawn.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 717px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e342b0efa333a72ce81426be21b67c7e/0ad97/no-sleep.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.29268292682927%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sleep deprived people\"\n        title=\"sleep deprived people\"\n        src=\"/static/e342b0efa333a72ce81426be21b67c7e/0ad97/no-sleep.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e342b0efa333a72ce81426be21b67c7e/85860/no-sleep.png 205w,\n/static/e342b0efa333a72ce81426be21b67c7e/d68e4/no-sleep.png 410w,\n/static/e342b0efa333a72ce81426be21b67c7e/0ad97/no-sleep.png 717w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">sleep deprived people</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n</li>\n<li>The over-prepared families who reaches the airport 5 hours early and still panics.</li>\n<li>The “business trip cool kids” carrying only a laptop bag like they own Wall Street.</li>\n<li>Newlyweds being cute &#x26; all, definitely en route to their honeymoon.</li>\n<li>Confused foreigners looking around like they opened the wrong video game map.</li>\n<li>That one aunty on the phone narrating every move: “Haanji, abhi boarding ho rahi hai…abhi gate pe khadi hoon…” (entire terminal knows her status).</li>\n<li>A couple with a baby, but they themselves look like they just finished 12th grade.</li>\n<li>All those 10/10s you’ll spot once, fall in love with, and never see again. Pain.</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>And finally, me:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Chose to board the flight instead of shooting my shot with that cute girl.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3a5e81ba6cbb6f4b403b606abb563bbd/0b533/approach.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 151.21951219512195%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"approach her or miss my flight\"\n        title=\"approach her or miss my flight\"\n        src=\"/static/3a5e81ba6cbb6f4b403b606abb563bbd/0b533/approach.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3a5e81ba6cbb6f4b403b606abb563bbd/85860/approach.png 205w,\n/static/3a5e81ba6cbb6f4b403b606abb563bbd/d68e4/approach.png 410w,\n/static/3a5e81ba6cbb6f4b403b606abb563bbd/0b533/approach.png 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">approach her or miss my flight</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Flying economy, normal boarding, because… reality check.</li>\n<li>Didn’t bother standing in line. Sat back, watched the chaos, and joined when the line disappeared.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 702px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/089ca1ae5cdc593083255a33cb0e4423/d6331/stay-seated.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.09756097560976%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"stay seated\"\n        title=\"stay seated\"\n        src=\"/static/089ca1ae5cdc593083255a33cb0e4423/d6331/stay-seated.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/089ca1ae5cdc593083255a33cb0e4423/85860/stay-seated.png 205w,\n/static/089ca1ae5cdc593083255a33cb0e4423/d68e4/stay-seated.png 410w,\n/static/089ca1ae5cdc593083255a33cb0e4423/d6331/stay-seated.png 702w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">stay seated</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Going to board now. AMA.</strong></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Order In Chaos At An Airport","date":"August 10, 2025","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/71f976a11af8f14910ef9ffa6c20d1a4/497c6/airport-chaos.png"}}},"slug":"order-in-chaos-at-an-airport","description":"A collection of raw, funny, and emotional observations while people-watching at an airport.","category":"Storytime","tags":["Life","Storytime","Travel","Observations"]},"timeToRead":3}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Order-In-Chaos-At-An-Airport/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Mistakes-To-Avoid-On-Fitness-Journey/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Mistakes To Avoid On Fitness Journey"}},"next":null}},
